s://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-36-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-37-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-38-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-39-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-40-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-41-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-42-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-43-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-44-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-45-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-46-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-47-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-48-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-49-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-50-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-51-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-52-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-53-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-54-).png","https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-55-).png"],"content":"<p>从昨天下午到今天上午，我所看到的是，现在上海正在轮番上演着各种热闹大戏，让人看得目不暇接。</p>\n<p>只是这精彩大戏之下，究竟有着多少人的苦痛，多少人的泪水，这就真的不好说了。</p>\n<p>昨晚九点四十左右，有上海网友爆出，现在已经是人心思离了，老外们都在陆续离开。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>底下已经有上海网友予以证实了，并且发出感叹。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-1-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>知名作家陈村则转了一个文章，说作者差一点离开这个人世间。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-2-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>陈村本人也确认这篇文章的确是他转载的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-3-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>上海财经大学退休教授陈顺霞的弟弟，也是小提琴家的陈顺平已经走了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-4-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>昨天凌晨，有网友透露了这样一个内幕。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-5-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>结果昨天早上八点半，新闻报道的数据果然分毫不差。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-6-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>大概是嫌还不够热闹，航天厂一把手也宣布退出志愿者工作。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-7-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这些都是杨海疑惑的地方。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-8-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>上海普通人们被折腾得太苦了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-9-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这让杨海开始怀疑自己工作的价值了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-10-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>徐汇区志愿者也表示不愿继续下去了，因为太折腾人了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-11-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这是当事志愿者心声的表达，让出示相关文件。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-12-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>张强医生也发声了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-13-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>还有上海网友画了这样一幅漫画。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-14-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>懂诗词的网友则来了这么一出。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-15-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>喜欢对联的网友也开始了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-16-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>喜欢添字的网友也来凑热闹了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-17-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>喜欢写对联的网友就是多，另一幅也火速出炉了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-18-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>喜欢成语的网友也不甘示弱。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-19-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>有网友不会诗词，但唱小调还是很在行的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-20-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>有网友在排队时看到了这个，瞬间沉默了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-21-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>底下的网友也是这么认为的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-22-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>严锋发起了这样的一个投票，结果投赞成票的有一万五千票，反对的则 2000 票，高达七比一的比例了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-23-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>以物换物的热潮则走向了更高潮。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-24-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这样的通知也贴出来了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-25-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>记性好的网友则搬出了这句台词。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-26-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>苏州的小区已经传来这样的消息。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-27-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>对此，知名作家刘心武表示不赞同，理由是不想看到上海苏州因为这事成为世仇。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-28-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>郎咸平则开始秀起了古文。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-29-).png\" alt=\"metanetworkusersmetaiostorage64029.png\"></p>\n<p>还有上海网友讲了发生在身边的一个段子。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-30-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这个段子也很有意思。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-31-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这个段子则让人心酸。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-32-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>上海本地网友则在发出这样的抱怨。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-33-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>有网友发了这样一个树洞。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-34-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>昨晚七点半左右，有医生网友在发出这样的提醒。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-35-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>当然也有网友在提醒大家这个。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-36-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>当然，更有意思的是这个事情，这是该网友大前天说的话。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-37-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>到了昨天晚上八点半左右，这个网友却急了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-38-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这个也让人觉得匪夷所思。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-39-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>网友们纷纷留下了这样的评论。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-40-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-41-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这个时候就体现出了共情的重要性。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-42-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>不过那批肉也的确存在问题，这是梅陇镇当地网友的反映。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-43-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这是网友提供的证据。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-44-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>梅陇镇网友真的很有勇气，不仅在微信群里说，还去微博上说了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-45-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>最后，梅陇镇的相关方面不得不出来致歉。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-46-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>有网友顺便普及了一下知识，真正能用来作油渣和红烧肉的是这种。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-47-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这个网友也很有意思。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-48-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>当然，为了让更多的上海普通市民吃上新鲜的肉和菜，不至于继续挨饿，京东这次也是真的拼尽全力了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-49-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这样的出征场面真的很悲壮了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-50-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这是京东为千千万万普通上海市民准备的物资。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-51-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>希望大家能记住他们的面容和眼晴，真的很大无畏了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-52-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这是他们在上海街头的背影。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-53-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>上海的胸外科医生王兴也是个很好的人，他发出这样的启事。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-54-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>并且大大方方的公布了自己的二维码。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-55-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>希望最后这个信息可以帮助到真正需要帮助的人。</p>\n<p>以上就是我观察到的在刚刚 24 小时里，在上海这座城市里所发生的种种事情，有悲伤，有沉痛，有黑色幽默，也有来自普通人的温情。</p>\n<p>不管怎样，希望我们都能记下这些所发生的事情，然后能够生活得更好，也活得足够坦然。</p>\n","more":"<p>从昨天下午到今天上午，我所看到的是，现在上海正在轮番上演着各种热闹大戏，让人看得目不暇接。</p>\n<p>只是这精彩大戏之下，究竟有着多少人的苦痛，多少人的泪水，这就真的不好说了。</p>\n<p>昨晚九点四十左右，有上海网友爆出，现在已经是人心思离了，老外们都在陆续离开。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>底下已经有上海网友予以证实了，并且发出感叹。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-1-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>知名作家陈村则转了一个文章，说作者差一点离开这个人世间。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-2-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>陈村本人也确认这篇文章的确是他转载的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-3-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>上海财经大学退休教授陈顺霞的弟弟，也是小提琴家的陈顺平已经走了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-4-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>昨天凌晨，有网友透露了这样一个内幕。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-5-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>结果昨天早上八点半，新闻报道的数据果然分毫不差。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-6-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>大概是嫌还不够热闹，航天厂一把手也宣布退出志愿者工作。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-7-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这些都是杨海疑惑的地方。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-8-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>上海普通人们被折腾得太苦了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-9-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这让杨海开始怀疑自己工作的价值了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-10-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>徐汇区志愿者也表示不愿继续下去了，因为太折腾人了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-11-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这是当事志愿者心声的表达，让出示相关文件。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-12-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>张强医生也发声了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-13-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>还有上海网友画了这样一幅漫画。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-14-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>懂诗词的网友则来了这么一出。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-15-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>喜欢对联的网友也开始了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-16-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>喜欢添字的网友也来凑热闹了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-17-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>喜欢写对联的网友就是多，另一幅也火速出炉了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-18-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>喜欢成语的网友也不甘示弱。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-19-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>有网友不会诗词，但唱小调还是很在行的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-20-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>有网友在排队时看到了这个，瞬间沉默了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-21-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>底下的网友也是这么认为的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-22-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>严锋发起了这样的一个投票，结果投赞成票的有一万五千票，反对的则 2000 票，高达七比一的比例了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-23-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>以物换物的热潮则走向了更高潮。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-24-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这样的通知也贴出来了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-25-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>记性好的网友则搬出了这句台词。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-26-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>苏州的小区已经传来这样的消息。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-27-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>对此，知名作家刘心武表示不赞同，理由是不想看到上海苏州因为这事成为世仇。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-28-).png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>郎咸平则开始秀起了古文。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://storageapi.fleek.co/andoroyur-team-bucket/metanetwork/users/metaio-storage/640-(-29-).png\" alt=\"metanetworkusersmetaiostorage64029.png\"></p>\n<p>还有上海网友讲了发生在身边的一个段子。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://st